						               													<description>Players compete to purchase vineyards along the Italian peninsula.&amp;#10;By exploiting their own lands, they will produce wine with which they will realize the revenue necessary to develop their own activities.&amp;#10;Who will become the most famous?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game is played in 6 turns.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each turn is divided into 3 phases:  &amp;#10;1.    The arrangement of the turn&amp;#10;2.    The choice of actions&amp;#10;3.    The development of actions&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The arrangement of the turn&amp;#10;Put 6 land cards on the table: get the first 4 from the stacks corresponding to the specific grape varieties. &amp;#10;Get the last 2 from the shared deck. These will be the lands that can be purchased in the turn.&amp;#10;For the successive turns, update the prices increasing the highest price to 7 and use the same gap for all other prices.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The choice of actions&amp;#10;Every player starting from the first will be able to do some actions. There is only one limit to the actions that can be done in a turn: that is the money necessary to do them.&amp;#10;These actions, that can be found on the corresponding table of the game board, are:  &amp;#10;Modify the game order for the next turn    &amp;#10;Turn a land into a DOCG area (where DOCG stays for &amp;ldquo;Denomination of origin inspected and guaranteed&amp;rdquo;)&amp;#10;Benefit from the events&amp;#10;Purchase the lands revealed on the turn&amp;#10;Develop your own production capacity (quantity)&amp;#10;Develop your general productive quality&amp;#10;Make one of your vineyards productive    &amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The development of actions&amp;#10;All the actions choosed before will be acted in the game, in the exact order of them.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;End of the game&amp;#10;The game ends at the end of the sixth turn.&amp;#10;In the last turn some bonus fame points will be distributed. &amp;#10;More specifically: fame points to the player who has got more points on the bonus vine production, fame points to the player who has got more lands for each of the 4 macro-areas, fame points to the player with more money, fame point for each line of the technological development equal to 3.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The winner is who has got more fame points.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
